channel.description:
We are Alltime10s and we aim to bring you the most informative, fascinating and engaging top 10 videos on YouTube.

Be sure to download the ALLTIME10S app here:
 iOS: http://itunes.apple.com/app/id981410231 
Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.creator.alltime10s

Don't be a stranger, drop us a line in the comments and let us know which videos you'd like us to make next or if we missed out any amazing facts. We really do enjoying reading everything you have to say.

A massive thanks to all of you for the support and love that you've shown us over the past couple of years! 
 
You might also enjoy some of our other channels:

Alltime Conspiracies - https://www.youtube.com/user/AlltimeConspiracies
Alltime Numbers - https://www.youtube.com/AlltimeNumbers

If you want more Alltime10s be sure to check out our favourite videos in this playlist: http://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLec1lxRhYOzt2qqqnFBIpUm63wr5yhLF6

Thanks, 
Dave and John
